title: General Motors to Participate in the Citi 2015 Global Technology Conference
text:
General Motors to Participate in the Citi 2015 Global Technology Conference Tue, Sep 8 2015 
General Motors will be participating in the Citi 2015 Global Technology Conference on Tuesday, September 8, 2015, in New York City, New York. GM's presentation will begin at approximately 1:15 PM ET followed by a Q&A session. Representing GM will be: 
Mike Ableson, Vice President of Global Planning & Program Management 
A live webcast of the presentation will be available on this page. Shortly before the webcast, the presentation materials will be posted here.
